<section id="produk" class="products section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-title">
			<h2>Produk Kami</h2>
			<p>Koleksi kopi pilihan dengan kualitas terbaik dan cita rasa yang tak terlupakan</p>
		</div>

		<div class="product-intro">
			<p>
				Agar pelanggan dapat menikmati rasa dan wangi kopi yang paling harum dan enak, disarankan untuk membeli secukupnya. 
				Kami sengaja menyangrai kopi pada hari yang sama dengan hari kopi dijual agar pelanggan dapat menikmati kopi yang harum. 
				Kopi yang dibeli disarankan untuk segera dikonsumsi dalam waktu 2 minggu - 1 bulan.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="products-grid">
			<div class="product-card">
				<div class="product-image">
					<div class="coffee-beans arabica"></div>
					<div class="product-badge">Premium</div>
				</div>
				<div class="product-content">
					<h3>Mokka Arabika</h3>
					<p class="product-subtitle">"Harum, memiliki kandungan asam yang lembut dan rendah kafein"</p>
					<p class="product-description">
						100% Kopi Arabika, gabungan dari Priangan, Jawa, Aceh, Medan, Flores dan Timor. 
						Kopi mentah disimpan selama 8 tahun dan disangrai menggunakan kayu selama 2 jam 
						sehingga menghasilkan wangi dan rasa yang khas.
					</p>
					
					<div class="product-options">
						<h4>Tersedia dalam bentuk:</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>Biji matang (roasted beans)</li>
							<li>Giling halus (fine grind) - Kopi Tubruk</li>
							<li>Giling medium (medium grind) - Espresso, French Press, V60</li>
							<li>Giling kasar (coarse grind) - Coffee Maker</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="pricing">
						<div class="price-option">
							<span class="weight">250 gram</span>
							<span class="price">Rp 50.000</span>
						</div>
						<div class="price-option">
							<span class="weight">500 gram</span>
							<span class="price">Rp 100.000</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="product-card">
				<div class="product-image">
					<div class="coffee-beans robusta"></div>
					<div class="product-badge">Strong</div>
				</div>
				<div class="product-content">
					<h3>Robusta</h3>
					<p class="product-subtitle">"Unggul di rasa pahit dan tinggi kafein"</p>
					<p class="product-description">
						100% Kopi Robusta, gabungan Robusta Sumatera dan Jawa. Kopi mentah dituakan 
						selama 5 tahun kemudian disangrai dengan kayu selama 2 jam untuk menghasilkan 
						karakter kuat yang khas Robusta.
					</p>
					
					<div class="product-options">
						<h4>Tersedia dalam bentuk:</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>Biji matang (roasted beans)</li>
							<li>Giling halus (fine grind) - Kopi Tubruk</li>
							<li>Giling medium (medium grind) - Espresso, French Press, V60</li>
							<li>Giling kasar (coarse grind) - Coffee Maker</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="pricing">
						<div class="price-option">
							<span class="weight">250 gram</span>
							<span class="price">Rp 40.000</span>
						</div>
						<div class="price-option">
							<span class="weight">500 gram</span>
							<span class="price">Rp 80.000</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="purchase-info">
			<div class="info-card">
				<h3>Informasi Pembelian</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Pembelian setiap pelanggan dibatasi maksimal 3 kg</li>
					<li>Kopi disangrai pada hari yang sama dengan hari penjualan</li>
					<li>Konsumsi dalam waktu 2 minggu - 1 bulan untuk kualitas terbaik</li>
					<li>Semua produk tanpa bahan kimia dan pengawet</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="#kontak" class="btn">Hubungi Kami</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.products {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
	}

	.product-intro {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.05);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;
	}

	.product-intro p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #555;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.products-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.product-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 16px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.product-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
	}

	.product-image {
		position: relative;
		height: 200px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.coffee-beans {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		position: relative;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.coffee-beans.arabica {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 50%, #CD853F 100%);
	}

	.coffee-beans.robusta {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3E2723 0%, #5D4037 50%, #6D4C41 100%);
	}

	.coffee-beans::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		width: 60%;
		height: 2px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.product-badge {
		position: absolute;
		top: 1rem;
		right: 1rem;
		background: #FFD700;
		color: #2d2d2d;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.product-content {
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.product-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #2d2d2d;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.product-subtitle {
		font-style: italic;
		color: #8B4513;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.product-description {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #555;
	}

	.product-options h4 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #2d2d2d;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	.product-options ul {
		list-style: none;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.product-options li {
		padding: 0.4rem 0;
		color: #555;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.product-options li::before {
		content: '●';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #8B4513;
	}

	.pricing {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.price-option {
		flex: 1;
		min-width: 120px;
		background: #f8f9fa;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.price-option:hover {
		border-color: #8B4513;
	}

	.weight {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #666;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.price {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #8B4513;
	}

	.purchase-info {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.info-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.info-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>') repeat;
		opacity: 0.3;
	}

	.info-card > * {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.info-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: #FFD700;
	}

	.info-card ul {
		list-style: none;
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 400px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.info-card li {
		padding: 0.6rem 0;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.info-card li::before {
		content: '✓';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #FFD700;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.products-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.product-content {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.pricing {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.price-option {
			min-width: auto;
		}

		.info-card {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.info-card h3 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
